Hello! Thank you for calling Sparkle Cleaners. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I’m interested in scheduling a cleaning service for my home.

Great! May I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jordan.

Nice to meet you, Jordan. Could I please know the size of your home in square feet?

Yes, it's approximately two thousand square feet.

Perfect. And could you also provide me with a contact phone number so we can confirm your appointment?

Of course, it's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Thank you, Jordan. We have all the information we need to schedule your cleaning service. We’ll reach out to confirm the details. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that’s all for now. Thanks, Alex.

You're welcome! Thank you for choosing Sparkle Cleaners. Have a great day!
